---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="下班後理財 | 白天努力生活，晚上規劃自由。"
    description="下班後理財是您最值得信賴的資產管理夥伴，提供專業、私密、直觀的資產追蹤工具。一站式管理您的全球資產。"
>
    <!-- SEO / GEO Structured Data -->
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
        {
            "@context": "https://schema.org",
            "@type": "FAQPage",
            "mainEntity": [
                {
                    "@type": "Question",
                    "name": "我的財務數據會被傳送到伺服器嗎？",
                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "完全不會。「下班後理財」是一個純前端運作的應用程式 (Client-side App)。所有的資料都加密儲存在您裝置的瀏覽器資料庫中，即使我們也無法看見您的資產狀況。"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "@type": "Question",
                    "name": "匯率是即時的嗎？",
                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "是的，系統每 5 分鐘會自動從國際匯率 API 獲取最新的匯率資訊。如果您的裝置處於離線狀態，系統會自動使用上一次更新的匯率進行計算。"
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    </script>
    <main
        class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-7xl relative z-10 min-h-screen"
    >
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <header class="text-center space-y-8 mb-32 animate-fade-in-down">
            <div
                class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4"
            >
                專業資產追蹤工具
            </div>
            <h1
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
            >
                <span
                    class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600"
                    >掌握財富，開啟自由人生</span
                >
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-700 tracking-wide mt-4"
            >
                白天努力生活，晚上規劃自由。
            </p>
            <p
                class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed mt-6"
            >
                整合現金、股票與房地產，即時掌握您的資產淨值與長期成長趨勢。
            </p>

            <!-- Bento Grid Section -->
            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full"
            >
                <!-- Assets Manager: Main Feature -->
                <a
                    href="/assets-manager"
                    class="group relative md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/50 to-indigo-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div
                            class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-blue-200"
                        >
                            💰
                        </div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight"
                        >
                            總資產計算機
                        </h2>
                        <p
                            class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md"
                        >
                            整合您的現金、股票與房地產，一眼掌握全球資產淨值與分佈。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-600 font-bold"
                    >
                        立即開始管理 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Compound Interest Calculator -->
                <a
                    href="/compound-interest"
                    class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6 border border-blue-500/30"
                        >
                            📈
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                            複利效應試算
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            見證時間的力量，計算您的長期投資收益與財富翻倍速度。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                    >
                        見證複利 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="16"
                            height="16"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </span>
                </a>

                <!-- Tax Saver Calculator -->
                <a
                    href="/tax-saver"
                    class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-white/20 text-white w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6 border border-white/30"
                        >
                            💰
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                            薪資節稅計算
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-emerald-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            智慧試算綜合所得稅，探索勞退自提、捐贈等節稅策略。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-white font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                    >
                        開始節稅 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="16"
                            height="16"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </span>
                </a>

                <!-- Coast FIRE & Rent vs Buy in a smaller grid or row -->
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:col-span-3"
                >
                    <!-- Coast FIRE Calculator -->
                    <a
                        href="/coast-fire"
                        class="group relative bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50/50 to-purple-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6"
                            >
                                🔥
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                                Coast FIRE 計算
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                計算何時能停止主動儲蓄，讓資產複利帶您抵達退休終點。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            探索未來 <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="16"
                                height="16"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                                ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                                ></polyline></svg
                            >
                        </span>
                    </a>

                    <!-- Rent vs Buy -->
                    <a
                        href="/rent-vs-buy"
                        class="group relative bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50/50 to-teal-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6"
                            >
                                🏠
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                                買房 vs 租房
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                考量稅率、投報率與維護成本，幫您做出最明智的居住決策。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="text-emerald-600 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            開始試算 <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="16"
                                height="16"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                                ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                                ></polyline></svg
                            >
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Site Introduction Section -->
        <section class="mt-24 mb-32 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-[3rem] p-8 md:p-16 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group"
            >
                <!-- Background Decorative Elements -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-[80px] opacity-50 group-hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full blur-[80px] opacity-50 group-hover:bg-emerald-200 transition-colors"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
                >
                    <div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight leading-tight"
                        >
                            掌握財務，<br />
                            <span class="text-blue-600"
                                >從下班後的五分鐘開始</span
                            >
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            「下班後理財」是專為台灣使用者打造的個人財務管理平台。我們深知財務規劃的複雜性，因此致力於開發直觀、專業且「隱私優先」的計算工具，幫助您在忙碌的生活中，輕鬆釐清資產現況並做出明智的決策。
                        </p>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div
                                    class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-1 shrink-0"
                                >
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                    資料全本地儲存
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div
                                    class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-1 shrink-0"
                                >
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                    即時匯率自動更新
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div
                                    class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-1 shrink-0"
                                >
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                    台灣稅制量身打造
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div
                                    class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-1 shrink-0"
                                >
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                    完全免費且無廣告
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
                        >
                            <div class="text-2xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                                安全隱私
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                不需註冊，您的資產數據永不離開瀏覽器，這是我們的最高承諾。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
                        >
                            <div class="text-2xl mb-4">🚀</div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                                多元工具
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                從基本的淨資產追蹤到複雜的稅務、退休規劃，一應俱全。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
                        >
                            <div class="text-2xl mb-4">📈</div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                                視覺回饋
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                不再只有冰冷的數字，透過量表與圖表幫助您直觀理解現況。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
                        >
                            <div class="text-2xl mb-4">☕</div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                                極致簡便
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                拋棄繁瑣的記帳，專注於大方向的財務健康與未來規劃。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    .animate-fade-in-down {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
</style>
